biography: Tommy, a formidable presence hailing from Espoo Ringside Golf, is known for his meticulous approach to the game. While outwardly calm, those who know Tommy best say that his intense focus and competitive spirit burn brightly beneath the surface.

Tommy is gearing up for his third appearance at the Hector Trophée in 2025. Although he is yet to capture the coveted Hector Trophée or the individual Victor Trophy, Tommy's dedication and strategic prowess make him one to watch in the upcoming tournament. His fans are waiting with baited breath to see if Tommy can finally bring home the win this time around.
